attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: This stunning sun filled 3 floor residence combines contemporary design with thoughtful details, offering the perfect urban retreat steps from everything that Southie has to offer. The spacious open-concept layout is perfect for entertaining, with high ceilings and beautiful hardwood floors throughout. Gourmet kitchen offers, Thermador appliances, custom cabinetry, quartz countertops & a generous island for dining and entertaining. Off the kitchen you will find two outdoor spaces; a balcony with a fire pit and complete view of the whole boston sky line, as well as a fenced in patio area with a dreamy hot tub. In addition to the primary suite are two more bedrooms that offer great flexibility for guests or a growing family & a space for a second living room, office, gym or playroom, and 2.5 more bathrooms. This home is perfectly located in the heart of Southie on top of "Pill Hill." a short walk to the seaport, beach and all of Southie's finest establishments.
